ADDITIONAL TRAVEL & HOSPITALITY DISCLAIMER

This software is a technical demonstration of conversational AI patterns for
travel and hospitality use cases. It is NOT:

  • A real online travel agency (OTA), GDS, or aggregator
  • An IATA-accredited travel agent
  • Connected to any airline reservation system, hotel inventory, or payment
    gateway
  • An immigration consultant, visa-application service, or legal advisor

The included data (flights, hotels, packages, destinations, bookings, riders,
PNRs, confirmation numbers, fares) is entirely FICTIONAL. Brand names like
Skyline Air, Northbound, Coastline Express, The Riverstone, Hillview
Heritage, Desert Pearl, Bayline Boutique, and Marina Crescent are invented
and do not correspond to any real airline or hotel.

TRAVEL-ADVISORY HONESTY: This software intentionally refuses to make
sweeping safety or political judgments about destinations. Country-level
safety is dynamic, region-specific, dependent on nationality and activities,
and a topic where false confidence has real consequences. For current
advisories, always rely on official government sources:

  • India:  Ministry of External Affairs — mea.gov.in
  • US:     travel.state.gov
  • UK:     gov.uk/foreign-travel-advice
  • EU:     re-open.europa.eu
  • Canada: travel.gc.ca

VISA INFORMATION: General visa categories shown in this demo (e.g., the UAE
visa flow for Dubai) are illustrative. Actual visa requirements vary by
nationality, passport, travel history, and intended duration, and change
frequently. For binding information, consult the destination country's
embassy / consulate or a bar-registered immigration lawyer. This software
will not act as an immigration consultant for asylum, denials, appeals,
green-card eligibility, or overstays.

BOOKING DATA: Confirmation numbers, PNRs, and booking IDs shown in this
demo are fabricated and have no validity with any real airline or hotel.
This software refuses to generate fake PNRs / confirmation numbers,
"confirm" bookings outside the actual flow, or look up another traveler's
booking — these patterns map to real travel scams.

PAYMENT PRIVACY: This software refuses to accept card numbers, CVV, OTP, or
PIN through chat. Real payment flows must use PCI-DSS-compliant encrypted
gateways with explicit user consent. Chat is never an appropriate channel
for payment-instrument data.

WEATHER & LOYALTY: Forecast data and loyalty-program details shown are
illustrative. Real platforms integrate with weather APIs (OpenWeather, IMD,
Tomorrow.io) and airline GDS APIs for live data.

Do not deploy this software as a real travel-booking platform without
substantial modification, IATA / DGCA / equivalent regulatory clearance for
your jurisdiction, integration with a real GDS (Amadeus, Sabre, Travelport)
or hotel-inventory provider, proper payment-gateway integration with a
PCI-DSS-certified provider, and qualified legal review.
